#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:4
msgid "Graphics Hardware"
msgstr "图形硬件的故障排除"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:6
msgid "Blender makes use of OpenGL, which is typically hardware accelerated."
msgstr "Blender 使用的是 OpenGL，这是非常典型的一种硬件加速技术。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:8
msgid ""
"This means issues with the graphics card hardware and drivers can impact on "
"Blender's behavior. This page lists some known issues using Blender on different "
"graphics hardware and how to troubleshoot them."
msgstr ""
"这意味着图形卡硬件或者驱动会影响到Blender的行为。本页列举了Blender在使用不同图形"
"硬件的时候引起的许多问题，并且告知如何排除这些故障。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:13
msgid "Performance"
msgstr "性能"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:15
msgid ""
"When the entire interface is very slow and unresponsive (*even* with the default "
"startup scene), this is likely a problem with the OpenGL configuration."
msgstr ""
"当整个界面非常缓慢且没有响应 ( *即使是默认的启动场景* )，这可能是 OpenGL 配置有问"
"题。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:18
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, in this situation, you may have to do some of your own tests to "
"find the cause. Below are some common causes and possible solutions."
msgstr ""
"不幸的是在这种情况，你可能要做一些你自己的测试来找出原因，这里是一些常见的原因和"
"可能的解决办法。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:22
msgid "Upgrade your OpenGL Driver"
msgstr "升级你的 OpenGL 驱动程序"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:22
msgid ""
"If you are experiencing any strange graphics problems with Blender, it is always "
"good to double check if you are using the latest drivers."
msgstr ""
"如果你在使用Blender时遇到任何奇怪的图形问题，请仔细检查你是否使用最新的驱动程序。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:24
msgid "Disable Anti-Aliasing :term:`FSAA, Multi-Sampling <FSAA>`"
msgstr "禁用抗锯齿 :term:`FSAA, 多重采样 <FSAA>`"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:25
msgid ""
"See :ref:`Invalid Selection, Disable Anti-Aliasing <troubleshooting-3dview-"
"invalid-selection>`."
msgstr ""
"请参见 :ref:`无效的选择、禁用抗锯齿 <troubleshooting-3dview-invalid-selection>`。"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:30
msgid "Change the *Window Draw Method*"
msgstr "更改 *窗口绘制方法*"

#: ../../manual/troubleshooting/gpu.rst:27
msgid ""
"This is set in the :ref:`system preferences <prefs-system-window-draw>`. It is "
"selected automatically, however, when experiencing problems it's worth checking "
"if changing this resolves interface drawing problems."
msgstr ""
"这是在 :ref:`用户设置 <prefs-system-window-draw>` 中的窗口绘制方法设置。它默认是"
"选择自动的，但是，在遇到问题时，应该检查是否改变设置可以解决界面绘制问题。"
